name: DELIVERY_GAS_SENT
description: This table contains documentation on the cord gasses that were sent, including specification of whether or not gases were sent. This information is entered in Stork's Delivery Summary activity and populated in the delivery record.

columns.name: SUMMARY_BLOCK_ID
columns.description: The unique identifier (.1 item) for the summary block record.

columns.name: LINE
columns.description: The line number for the information associated with this record. Multiple pieces of information can be associated with this record.

columns.name: BIRTH_GASES_SENT_C_NAME
columns.description: The sent cord gas category ID for the delivery record.
